pageProduct.name: Swisse Organic Vitex 1500mg 60 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Ultiboost High Strength Organic Vitex is a premium quality, high strength formula to support female reproductive health.

Female Reproductive Health: This formula contains organic vitex, which has been traditionally used in Western Herbal Medicine to support female reproductive health. It also helps maintain female hormone balance. Menstrual Cycle Regulation: Vitex has been traditionally used in Western Herbal Medicine to help regulate the menstrual cycle and stabilise irregular periods.

PMS Symptom Relief: Vitex has been traditionally used in Western Herbal Medicine to help relieve common symptoms of PMS including tension, moodiness, irritability, bloating, fluid retention and headaches. It has also been used in traditional Western Herbal Medicine to help relieve breast pain and swelling associated with the premenstrual period.

Menopause Symptom Relief: Vitex helps relieve and reduce the occurrence of menopausal symptoms such as irritability, mood swings, night sweats and excessive perspiration from hot flushes.

Certified Organic: Swisse Ultiboost High Strength Organic Vitex contains certified organic vitex agnus-castus. Swisse Ultiboost High Strength Organic Vitex has been formulated based on scientific and traditional evidence to provide a high strength organic vitex formula in a convenient, one-a-day dose.

Size: 60 Tablets

Warnings

If symptoms persist consult your healthcare practitioner. If fluid retention persists - seek medical advice.

IMPORTANT INFORMATION

No added lactose, gluten, yeast, egg, soy or artificial flavours. Suitable for vegetarians.

Ingredients

VITEX (Vitex agnus-castus) extract equiv. dry fruit: 1.5 g

Directions

Adult Dosage: One tablet daily upon waking, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C. Do not use if cap seal is broken.
